Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico

Terrace views are amazing, but think of Turkish breakfasts with the view of the Hagia Sophia and Bosphorus at the Henna Istanbul Hotel. 😍  Elevate your stay by indulging in authentic Turkish cuisine before you explore the heart of the old city and its attractions. 🕌 

💡 BH tip: Visit the Grand Bazaar. Just make sure to explore first before buying your souvenirs; you will see more unique finds at every turn!

Have you visited Turkey? Is it part of your bucket list? 🇹🇷 

📍 @istanbul_henna, Istanbul, Turkey

node.text:
Rediscovering Bali with @explorerssaurus. 🇮🇩 The Kamandalu Resort gives couples a gorgeous backdrop to a special romantic getaway with their infinity pools overlooking lush treetops. It sure looks cozy and luxurious, but there is so much more to do. If you're wondering if there is something else to look forward to apart from some R&R, ask the staff about their leisure offerings! 😎

Choose your adventure: Ayung white water rafting, Mount Batur sunrise hike, and an ATV ride sounds perfect for adrenaline junkies. For the more laidback, opt for the culinary journey, bird watching, or a private yoga session! 🧘

Have you been to Indonesia? What's the best experience you've had there? 😍

📽️ @explorerssaurus_
📍 @kamandalu, Bali, Indonesia
🎶 Sarcastic Sounds - I Can't Help

Wouldn't it be awesome to crack a cold one by the bonfire? 🍻 Swipe to see what's waiting for you at BNBBreeze!

Are cabin stays something you'd go for? Would you stay here? 😍

📸 @levimkelly

Sunsets like these are paired with margaritas, don't you think? 🍹 At Hotel Casa Las Tortugas, experience barefoot living in one of Mexico's "home away from home". With their sustainable practices, your trip will bring you closer to nature while you create new memories without leaving any carbon footprint.

With cozy rooms facing a gorgeous sea, lounge comfortably in your own outdoor hammock and embrace the beach life, guilt-free. 🌊

💡 BH Tip: If you're the type to just lounge in your room to watch TV the whole day, Hotel Casa Las Tortugas doesn't have them. We recommend trying kiteboarding instead! 😉

Are you a beach bum or a holiday thrill-seeker? What's something you haven't tried doing while on holiday? We'd love to know!

📍 @casalastortugas, Holbox, Mexico
🎶 Sumeru - islandman

node.text:
Wishing for peaceful mornings? 😌 At Amanyara, mornings are always better in their stylish yet homey pavilions and villas. In this secluded paradise located on the shores of an 18,000-acre nature reserve, you are miles away from deadlines, traffic, and making decisions throughout the day. You may need to decide between breakfast by the pool or on your private patio though! ☕

Want to be "one with nature"? Amanyara's partnership with Sustainable Oceans International gives guests a chance to give back to Mother Nature through their Adopt-A-Coral initiatives aimed at restoring and protecting coral reefs. 🌅 

Have you visited Turks and Caicos? 🇹🇨 What is your most favorite memory here? 😍 

📍 @amanyara_resort, Northwest Point, Turks and Caicos Islands

Entering the secret doors to this luxury villa in Seychelles with @daynabolden. 💦 Looking for a summer getaway with the family? These spacious accommodations at the Le Duc de Praslin Hotel & Villas can comfortably sleep up to 8 adults and 4 children. It also has a private magna infinity pool for unlimited fun! 👨‍👩‍👧

Is Seychelles on your travel list for the year? Who are you bringing with you? 🛩️ 

📽️ @daynabolden

Toasting to this view of New York with @dwanderess at The Williamsburg Hotel. 🗽 Have you been to the city that never sleeps? 🌇 

NYC is such a beautiful and diverse place where you can turn your dreams into reality! ✨ Be part of intriguing experiences that can only be found here like the “Astro Pizza Night” for mystic pizza specials that change with every astrological season. 🌠 

💡 BH tip: Here for business? Book the Work + Workout Suite that comes with a dedicated workspace and a digital Liteboxer workout system. 💪🏻

People watching at The Lost Poet while enjoying these freshly baked croissants with @prettylittlelondon! 🥐 This charming four-bedroom townhouse along the charming streets of Portobello Road is the perfect stay for those who are looking for a central location minus the crowded corridors of a hotel. 🏠

With small touches like a stocked refrigerator for guests and exclusive discounts at nearby restaurants, this newly opened gives you everything that you need to make you feel like a true Londoner. 🇬🇧 

💡 BH tip: Enter the new normal of checking in with the Flexipass App that allows contactless check-in and access to the building with a few taps on your mobile phone. Remote staff is online 24/7 to also answer inquiries via text. 

Have you been to London before? Let us know your travel experience during your last visit! 💂🏻

Reliving these quiet Greek mornings with @momentsofgregory at the Bill & Coo Suites & Lounge. 😌 Are you also dreaming of this sea view escape? 💦 

This breathtaking stay overlooking the Megali Ammos Bay is an intimate adults-only hotel that is literally a few steps from the bustling streets of Mykonos where you can be one with the locals and just bask in the famous hospitality of the Greeks. 🇬🇷 

💡 BH tip: Looking for a few things to add to your itinerary while you’re here? Check out the Archaeological Museum of Mykonos for the museum geeks, Kalogera Street for the shopaholics, and the Panagia Paraportianin for architecture enthusiasts. 🏛️ 

Have you been to Greece before? Share your travel hacks with us below! 

📸 @momentsofgregory
📍 @billandcoowayoflife, Greece

Enjoying our summer days in Egypt with @_dgtravel_ at the Tamra Beach Resort. 😎 Swipe to see the epic view of the Red Sea! 🌊 

Located just a few minutes away from the Sharm ElSheikh International Airport, this expansive resort makes you feel right at home with its 305 rooms that range from luxury suites to family-friendly accommodations. 👨‍👩‍👧

💡 BH tip: Book a table at the Ristorante Di Palma for a sumptuous meal of fresh seafood by the glistening sea.

When was the last time that you had a similar view for breakfast? Share your travel experiences with us below! ☀️ 

📸 @_dgtravel_
📍 @tamra_beach_resort, Sharm El Sheikh, Egypt
